Critical priority
* Add PAM authentication support.
* Add NLS support.
* Move primitive gui code to new class.
* Fork the GUI process and drop privileges.
* Let the GUI and the authentication code communicate through IPC

Moderate priority
* Document functions.
* Allow for scaled/centered background.
