* Add buttons and animations.
* Replace Imlib2 with own functions.
* Add XDM-AUTHORIZATION-1.

Low priority
* Add support for runtime theme switching.
* Add support for multiple sessions.
* Add support for actions other than login (shutdown, hibernate).
